Package: semanticsmith
Type: Package
Title: Semantic Smith-Waterman Local Alignment for Text
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Performs local sequence alignment on tokenized text using
    the Smith-Waterman algorithm with arbitrary word similarity functions.
    Supports affine gap penalties via a shared C core for performance.
